      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"quickly resolved\"? the scan specifically flagged this as a critical vulnerability that requires a full reboot and offline patching process. we're talking at least a 6-hour window where the portal is totally dark. if we stay online and someone exploits this before the patch is ready, the fallout will be massive. are you sure you aren't downplaying the urgency just to avoid the downtime?",
